    "For a fair model comparison, all methods utilizing pre-trained models Evaluation Metrics.",
    "We employ widely used two standard metrics in DIL [44], average classification accuracy (AA) and forgetting rate (AF) as the evaluation metrics for comparing the CP-Prompt and other baselines.",
    "Experimental ResultsMain Results.",
    "Experimental results from Table 1, 2 and 3 demonstrate that our proposed CP-Prompt method significantly outperforms other exemplar-free methods, including the recently introduced state-of-the-art domain incremental method S-liPrompt.",
    "We slightly extend the Dual-Prompt and HiDe-Prompt to adopt to the DIL setting."
